Package edu.umd.cs.dmonner.tweater.util

Class Summary
AlertEmailer A class that reads email information from a Properties object and can thereafter send email message alerts.
NumberRange Represents a range of integers, inclusive on either end.
NumberSet Represents a possibly discontinuous set of integers as a collection of NumberRange objects.
OneLineFormatter A simple formatter for log records that specifies date, time, level, and message on a single line (with the exception of multi-line messages).
Properties An extension of Java's default Properties class with extra convenience methods for returning values as types other than String as well as requiring that values be present.
Setup Walks the user through the process of logging in to Twitter to obtain an access token, which is a prerequisite for using the Streaming API.
Util Provides static constants and utility functions for use in other classes.
